OL,4,C27 times is convicted of murder
OL,6,FA man who knifed his girlfriend 27
OL,7,Ftimes and claimed it was "self
OL,8,Fdefence" has been unanimously
OL,9,Fconvicted of murder by a jury in
OL,10,FLiverpool.
OL,12,FMichael Ormandy, 34, attacked 32-year
OL,13,Fold Rebekah Campbell after breaking
OL,14,Finto her flat in Huyton, last April.
OL,16,FHis trial at Liverpool Crown Court
OL,17,Fheard Ormandy, a drug dealer and
OL,18,Fformer cage fighter from Litherland,
OL,19,Fwas wearing a bulletproof vest when he
OL,20,Flaunched the brutal attack.
