OL,3,CAbusive boyfriend who knifed Rebekah
OL,4,C27 times is convicted of murder
OL,6,FPhone records revealed a friend heard
OL,7,FRebekah plead "go away, Mick" before
OL,8,Fthe line went dead.
OL,10,FCCTV captured Ormandy leaving the
OL,11,Fscene as Rebekah, critically injured,
OL,12,Fstaggered outside, telling neighbours,
OL,13,F"My fella stabbed me," before
OL,14,Fcollapsing.
OL,16,FDespite police efforts, she died in
OL,17,Fhospital a few hours later.
