OL,3,CAbusive boyfriend who knifed Rebekah
OL,4,C27 times is convicted of murder
OL,6,FThe murder followed a history of
OL,7,Fdomestic abuse within the
OL,8,Frelationship, including an incident
OL,9,Fjust days before the murder in which
OL,10,FOrmandy punched Rebekah during a night
OL,11,Fout, leaving her with a black eye.
OL,13,FAfter the stabbing, he called police,
OL,14,Fthreatening to "blow everyone up" with
OL,15,Fa purported suicide vest.
OL,17,FOrmandy's defence put forward that he
OL,18,Facted in self-defence, despite a post-
OL,19,Fmortem revealing Rebekah suffered 18
OL,20,Fstab wounds and nine slashes - many of
OL,21,Fwhich were defensive injuries.
